headline: 2 Dividend Growth Stocks to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: The two healthcare companies below generally deliver excellent returns and dividend growth.  Consider the following two healthcare leaders: Zoetis (NYSE: ZTS) and Eli Lilly (NYSE: LLY).  Zoetis is a leading animal health company with a diverse portfolio of products spanning various categories, including livestock, companion animals, and more.
